text: Atte Lindqvist (20 October 1894 - 26 June 1972) was a Finnish diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Finnish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Finland Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vyborg
